videos.description: Cassius Winston finds a lane and bursts to the rim, evading Indiana defenders on his way to a nice finger-roll finish with the left hand.
videos.headline: Winston slices through defense for smooth finish

videos.description: Cassius Winston makes a beautiful cross-court pass to Aaron Henry, who rises up for the emphatic one-handed jam in transition.
videos.headline: Henry reaches back for huge fast-break jam

videos.description: Romeo Langford drives and dishes to Jake Forrester, who goes around Xavier Tillman to put down a rim-rocking two-handed flush.
videos.headline: Forrester throws down big slam for Indiana

videos.description: Cassius Winston drives into the lane and gets off a scoop shot under Jake Forrester's arm, somehow getting the roll for a tough bucket.
videos.headline: Winston connects on circus finish

videos.description: Cassius Winston spins away from Devonte Green and lobs it up for Xavier Tillman, who finishes the alley-oop with a big two-handed jam.
videos.headline: Winston lobs, Tillman slams

videos.description: Cassius Winston swings a pass to Kenny Goins, who swishes a triple to put the Spartans ahead by 1 with under a minute to play.
videos.headline: Goins gives MSU late lead with clutch 3

videos.description: Romeo Langford drives to the rim and banks one home over two Michigan State defenders to give Indiana a 1-point lead late in the 2nd half.
videos.headline: Langford responds with go-ahead finish

videos.description: Cassius Winston tries to lay in the game-tying bucket, but Justin Smith gets a fingertip on it to protect Indiana's lead in the closing seconds of overtime.
videos.headline: Smith blocks Winston's game-tying layup in final seconds of OT

videos.description: Cassius Winston sparks the Spartans with a 26-point performance, but it's not enough to outlast the Hoosiers, who snap a seven-game losing skid.
